	(text ">[!NOTE]\n> The Olimex ESP32-POE is not galvanically isolated. \n> --- Do not plug in Via USB while powered via POE.\n>\n> The Olimex ESP32-POE-ISO is galvanically isolated, \n> and can be plugged in via USB & POE simultaneously."
