	(text "The I2C bus connection is used by \nthe ADE7953, but here are 2 more \nthat add more extensibility to the \nboard as a whole. One of these will \nmay be used by a PN532 RFID Card Reader. \n---\nNOTE: Cut jumpers & solder in THT \nresistors if you find the I2C data\nhas a bad rise-time/ connection."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 64.516 71.12 0)
